data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the coveted Kukanono neighborhood! This exceptional 4-bedroom, 4-bathroom residence offers an array of features designed for comfort, versatility, and luxurious living. As you enter, you're greeted by a sense of space that effortlessly connects the various living areas. The heart of the home is a gracious living room that spills into the kitchen creating an ideal space for gatherings and everyday living Enter through the private entryway to discover a unique 4th bedroom that can be transformed into an office or a living space. Complete with its own bathroom and potential kitchen unit, this flexible arrangement is perfect for multigenerational families or those seeking a dedicated workspace. Close to Castle Hospital, commuting is a breeze with easy access to Pali Highway. Kailua town is within reach, offering a wealth of shopping, dining, and recreational opportunities. Look no further if you're seeking an unparalleled blend of location, versatility, and value. This remarkable home in the Kukanono neighborhood is your ticket to luxurious living. An assumable loan option available at 4.49% contingent upon the Seller's VA eligibility being released.
